en.Description: Stunning Executive Cottage located just steps to elementary school, park, community pool & bus stop. This beautiful 5 bedroom home features newly renovated Kitchen with high end appliances, gorgeous new bathrooms, strip wood floors on main level, finished basement w/ 3rd bathroom, new windows, newer electric furnace & heat pump and more!
